### Add content
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{$randomInt 10 20}}",
  "title": "Cows",
  "status": "IDEA",
  "desc": "Video about cows",
  "contentType": "VIDEO",
    "dateCreated": "{{$localDatetime 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:26.7522291' 3 d}}",
